Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:09.79,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:20.32,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.51,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:06.99,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:14.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:20.99,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:28.43,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be too\Ndangerous to sit back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and do nothing about\Nthat mobile air base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:40.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are hereby sending the Chor\NTempest on a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Messis shall serve\Nas the relay point...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:45.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if we discover the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,That will be left to\Nyour discretion, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:52.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do believe you have the capacity\Nto blow it up at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why do you think they\Ntook you off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's something that I\Ncan't quite put my finger on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,And what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I promised not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:35.80,Titles,,90,0,0,,Sibylla
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,As if Sibylla Aer would\Never do as she's told.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you really\Ngoing to let this go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this makes me wonder\Nwhat the sibyllae are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:59.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I would give for that\Nkind of single-minded passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning\Nof that Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:12.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe it's Sibylla\NAer and Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer and Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,After Chor Rubor was\Ndisbanded, these two sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...were assigned to the\NMessis as your replacements...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and have been on\Nreconnaissance duty ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all that we have\Nto offer at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,We heard about Dominüra and Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,But where are Aer and Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:04:00.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two will be\Nsitting out this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:03.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,There'll be plenty of\Ntime to discuss that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, won't you\Nplease come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should go over the\Ndetails of our mission, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,First of all, I'd like\Nyou to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a little early,\Nbut I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll meet you in the\Ndining room in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:24.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll be along soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Roatre!\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, you were\Ntaking so long, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your braids are\Nstarting to come undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll fix them for you.\NWe still have time anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those Simouns we\Nsaw at the Ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...do you think they've made it\Nback to the highlands' base station?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:25.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're paired up with Morinas,\Nand she's an excellent auriga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,And even if something\Nshould go wrong somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'll be there to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is just a reconnaissance\Nmission after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It would be better if we could avoid\Ngoing into battle at all, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,That would be the\Nbest of all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the data these two\Nhave gathered on patrol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:58.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we've narrowed down the Shoukoku\Nair base's approximate location...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to this region right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,In those defenseless Similes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, we two will\Nhold the rearguard position...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:10.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and relay all\Ncommunications from the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest is up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no getting around the fact\Nthat the gap between the Similes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the Simouns in terms\Nof mobility is far too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Putting together a mixed unit like\Nthis... It's just not feasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,There you go making rash\Npromises again, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you knock it off?\NBoth of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Alty's the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's try to get along, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're comrades. We all\Nate from the same pot, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say it, Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, don't mind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please continue, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,First, we'll have the\Nmembers of Chor Tempest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That Mamina's changed, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the way, what did you\Nnot want her to say, Roatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,The mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knew Vura was flying\Nreconnaissance in a Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:12.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, and to make sure their\Nefforts don't go to waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the rest of us need to be\Nin top form during this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, this is where\Nwe're supposed to deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we're going to proceed\Naccording to plan. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:50.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can the center deploy\NChor Tempest in this state?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:54.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just as Sibylla\NDominüra said to me once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,The center understands nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:03.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will be a while before\NChor Tempest returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like you both to get\Nsome rest while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:10.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's part of our duty\Nto rest... correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's correct, Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't miss any\Nsigns of Chor Tempest's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to reiterate\Nthat to the patrol unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:32.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,They forbade you from attending\NAnglas's funeral, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:35.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is rather harsh of our\Ncountry, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more tenuous a state\Nthey find themselves in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:44.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the more people try to cling to\Nthe comfort of their conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:49.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina, I can see that\Nyou've changed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:58.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I'm detaching the cables for\Nthe time being." So she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,How annoying is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,So they must be having a private\Nconversation one adult to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I say leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,3 o'clock! There's a huge shadow\Nin that break in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep the\Ncommunication cables intact...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and approach from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:31.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we've found the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those Simouns we encountered\Nat the Ruins could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should find out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:37.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's just confirm that\Nbefore we head home, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't let down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's a chance that the enemy\Ncould be patrolling this area too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we go much farther, we'll be\Nleaving the patrol area, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we\Nshould be heading back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:38.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to our rendezvous\Npoint with the regina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's patrol this\Narea a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,There it is! The Messis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the rear of our ship.\NA single Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Approaching at a rapid pace.\NIt's a Chor Tempest Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Aer and Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought we'd\Nfind Vura on board the Messis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's quite surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was worried\Nabout that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer and Sibylla\NYun, please go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought they might show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's head that way ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:57.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Channel all power from the\Nhelical motors to the engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're heading for the\Npatrol zone at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're heading toward the\Nrendezvous point with the regina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Right!\N— Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, they've spotted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Retreat at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shark Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger! Shark Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't shake them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those guys are way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,She just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril just told us\Nto make a run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should do as she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, both our\NSimouns will be shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry back\Nand let the others know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:30.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. We'll come\Nback for you as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please have no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:04.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can understand what I'm\Nsaying, then listen to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing but\Nan unknown sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,...doomed to die in\Nsuch a place as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do I care\Nabout my own life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:19.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Behind me lies the finest sibylla\Nin all of Simulacrum Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Aurea Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm getting her out\Nof here no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,And not one of you will lay\Nso much as a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Both the sibylla behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you yourself are\Nthe finest of all sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:40.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,You two are sibyllae\Nfrom Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no one closer\Nto God than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,In our nation,\Nthe Plumbum highlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you are respected\Nabove all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:54.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is not our choice to\Nengage in battle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:58.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it is not our will to\Ncapture an injured sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses of\Nthe Plumbum Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:08.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're not the same as the Shoukoku\Nsoldiers on board this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:12.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,The battle we have just\Nbeen waging is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no longer any\Nreason for us to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, you must believe us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we were planning\Nto capture you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then there would be no need\Nfor us to go to all these lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What those priestesses\Nare telling us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am sure it is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, you must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come, together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's what's\Ngoing to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you four let us get\Naway from this base...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you'll have nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. If they capture you,\Nyou are certain to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:45.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You four recognized\Nme as a true sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:51.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if you let me escape, you'll\Nbe put to death as traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Farewell, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:34.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're planning to go to your\Ndeath at the hands of those soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me say it in your language...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've sighted a huge\Nshadow straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain, we believe it's\NShoukoku's aerial base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it appears to be on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, take your\Npositions for battle level one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, take your\Npositions for battle level one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace\Nyourself for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, brace\Nyourself for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're going\Nto the priestesses' aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry back\Nto the Messis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:41.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,— No!\N— Step back, Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,— You're in our way!\N— Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go, Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry too, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:56.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to get away from\Nhere! We've got to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:22:00.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to just stand\Nhere forever, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:24.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:47.95,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:52.18,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:59.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:06.85,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:19.74,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:24.92,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:28.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:32.93,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:38.80,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.34,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:47.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:53.44,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:59.67,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.67,Titles,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was a proud sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:11.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...not to mention just a young\Ngirl from Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:13.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now Sibylla Mamina is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:17.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lament.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.02,Titles,,0,0,0,,Lament
